Worried that you might think it strange

20
00:01:39,057 --> 00:01:41,685
Though I couldn’t express everything in the writing

21
00:01:42,686 --> 00:01:46,523
As written in the text, at first it was curiosity

22
00:01:48,859 --> 00:01:50,736
Now, it's genuine

