00:03:24,496 --> 00:03:25,622
This part..

35
00:03:25,997 --> 00:03:28,667
It would be better if it were smoothed out, right?

36
00:03:29,417 --> 00:03:30,669
Just a moment.

37
00:03:41,346 --> 00:03:42,180
How about now?

38
00:03:44,391 --> 00:03:47,853
Oh, it really feels smoother now.

39
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,730
Mr. Choi Jaemin,

40
00:03:50,897 --> 00:03:53,525
What are you going to do with me? You should use this opportunity.

41
00:04:00,157 --> 00:04:02,868
In my opinion, a personal statement

42
00:04:02,868 --> 00:04:04,244
shouldn't be written

43
00:04:04,244 --> 00:04:05,620
with the intent of just trying to impress others.

44
00:04:06,997 --> 00:04:08,707
Hmm.. then what?

45
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:13,128
It should naturally show that

46
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:15,672
you are proud of yourself through the writing.

47
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:17,174
Like..

48
00:04:17,174 --> 00:04:18,884
Does it convey sincerity?

49
00:04:19,885 --> 00:04:21,136
A forced, fabricated piece of writing

50
00:04:21,136 --> 00:04:22,971
is something the reader can also feel.

51
00:04:23,638 --> 00:04:25,140
Awkward and exaggerated

52
00:04:26,349 --> 00:04:27,726
Hmm..

53
00:04:30,061 --> 00:04:32,647
You must have at least one part you're confident in

54
00:04:32,647 --> 00:04:35,650
It would be good to focus on appealing that

55
00:04:38,153 --> 00:04:39,112
Yes

56
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,158
Ah.. why

57
00:04:43,408 --> 00:04:44,242
Because it's cute

58
00:04:52,209 --> 00:04:53,501
Oppa

59
00:04:55,378 --> 00:04:57,464
Hey, what are you doing here?

60
00:04:57,672 --> 00:04:58,632
Sangmyeong Oppa said

61
00:04:58,632 --> 00:05:00,300
Oppa usually works here

62
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:01,509
Came looking for Oppa

63
00:05:02,427 --> 00:05:04,221
He wouldn’t even eat when I asked

64
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,557
Who? A friend?

65
00:05:07,557 --> 00:05:09,684
Yeah, my classmate Jaemin

66
00:05:09,684 --> 00:05:11,019
Oh, hello

67
00:05:13,688 --> 00:05:15,899
All of Oppa's friends are handsome

68
00:05:16,691 --> 00:05:17,776
Can I sit?

69
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,361
Sure

70
00:05:47,973 --> 00:05:48,598
Ah

71
00:05:49,015 --> 00:05:52,936
Oppa was really popular in college, you know?

72
00:05:53,228 --> 00:05:56,481
All my friends lined up asking to be introduced

73
00:05:56,481 --> 00:05:57,440
Hey!

74
00:05:57,774 --> 00:05:59,359
It wasn't that much, you know?

75
00:05:59,359 --> 00:06:00,986
What lineup?

76
00:06:01,361 --> 00:06:02,570
So you’re not busy, then

77
00:06:02,570 --> 00:06:04,572
Why won’t you eat with me?

78
00:06:04,906 --> 00:06:06,908
You’re busy

79
00:06:06,908 --> 00:06:08,285
I’m not busy, you know?

80
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:09,286
Look at this

81
00:06:09,286 --> 00:06:11,454
Always making excuses to avoid me

82
00:06:13,915 --> 00:06:15,041
Do you have a lover

83
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:17,585
Hidden away somewhere?

84
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:22,132
Ah.. I guess?

85
00:06:23,049 --> 00:06:24,009
Hey, whether I have a lover or not

86
00:06:24,009 --> 00:06:25,635
What’s it to you?

87
00:06:25,635 --> 00:06:26,052
What’s it to you

88
00:06:27,971 --> 00:06:28,680
Or not

89
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,515
But are you doing well at work?

90
00:06:30,598 --> 00:06:32,017
Yes, of course

91
00:06:32,017 --> 00:06:34,311
Do you know how much my seniors adore me?

92
00:06:35,854 --> 00:06:38,023
Hey, are you working at JK Company? Are you preparing for that?

93
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:39,941
Ah..

94
00:06:40,525 --> 00:06:43,403
Oh, oppa, are you also preparing to apply to our company?

95
00:06:44,904 --> 00:06:47,240
If so, I'll give you some job application tips.

96
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,950
Can I have your number?

97
00:06:51,494 --> 00:06:52,871
What kind of trick is this?

98
00:06:53,538 --> 00:06:55,165
Is this a new type of flirting or what?

99
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:03,131
Ah!

100
00:07:03,465 --> 00:07:04,174
Crazy..

101
00:07:04,174 --> 00:07:05,759
