102
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,426
I need to go.

103
00:07:06,426 --> 00:07:08,178
Hey, you work a part-time job too?

104
00:07:08,178 --> 00:07:09,095
Yeah, just for today.

105
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:11,556
Ah, that's not what's important right now.

106
00:07:12,474 --> 00:07:14,642
Oppa, can you drop me off just up ahead?

107
00:07:15,143 --> 00:07:16,728
Hey, are you a child?

108
00:07:17,103 --> 00:07:19,022
Ah, why? It's been a while since we last met.

109
00:07:19,022 --> 00:07:20,148
Just to the taxi stand.

110
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:20,648
Huh?

111
00:07:23,276 --> 00:07:24,152
I’ll drop you off and come back.

112
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:28,198
Ah, you really are tiring.

113
00:07:29,491 --> 00:07:30,075
Let's go.

114
00:07:30,116 --> 00:07:31,242
See you next time.

115
00:07:31,826 --> 00:07:32,410
Yes.

116
00:07:45,340 --> 00:07:47,926
honey.

